'''Aletta Bezuidenhout''' (yavutse ku ya 17 Gicurasi 1949), ni umukinnyi [[Kenya|wa]] filime [[Afurika y’Epfo|ukomoka muri]] Kenya wavukiye muri [[Kenya]], umwanditsi akaba n'umukinnyi wa filime. <ref>https://www.fernsehserien.de/aletta-bezuidenhout/filmografie</ref> <ref>http://www.filmstarts.de/personen/103650.html</ref> Akora azwi  muri productions ya :''Weerskant die Nag'', ''Committed'' and ''Spoon'', ''Lament for Koos'' and ''Mother Courage''.''.'' <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/aletta-bezuidenhout</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 17 Gicurasi 1949 i [[Nairobi]] muri [[Kenya]]. Se yari injeniyeri. Yakoraga mu Nama Njyanama ya Transvaal yubuhanzi (Truk). Yatoje kandi arangiza BA Drama muri kaminuza ya Cape Town. <ref name="esat">https://esat.sun.ac.za/index.php/Aletta_Bezuidenhout </ref>

Yashakanye n'umucuranzi Colin Shamley, icyo gihe umukinnyi Tertius Meintjes nyuma na Anthony Perris. <ref name="esat">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://esat.sun.ac.za/index.php/Aletta_Bezuidenhout "Aletta Bezuidenhout career"]. esat<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">4 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref><ref>https://esat.sun.ac.za/index.php/Aletta_Bezuidenhout</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yize ikinamico muri kaminuza ya Cape Town nyuma atangira umwuga we wo gukina i Kruik. Nyuma, yimukiye muri old Transvaal  akora muri Sosiyete na Theatre y'Isoko. Hagati aho, yakoraga mu nama nyinshi zo mu karere zishinzwe ubuhanzi, nka 'Truk en Kruik'. Nyuma yaje gutangira gutoza abandi bakinnyi.<ref>http://performance.rovere.com/dnxma/tertius-meintjes-wikipedia</ref> 

Mu 1970, yagaragaye muri ''The Space'' nyuma aza gukorana na ''Dusa Stas Fish'' na ''Vi'', ''The Resistible Rise of Arturo UI'' and ''Treats'' . Mu 1974, yashinze isosiyete ikora, 'The Company'. Hagati aho, yagize uruhare mu ikinamico akina amakinamico nka ''Desire'', ''Mother Courage'' in 1977, ''Women of Troy'', ''Lament for Koos'' and ''The Minotaur's Sister'' mu 1985.  <ref name="tvsa">https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=611</ref><ref>https://thenation.co.za/bio/aletta-bezuidenhout-biography/</ref>

Usibye gukina, yakoraga nk'umwanditsi w'amakinamico kandi akora ''Time of Footsteps'', ''Silent Envelope'', ''Angel in a Dark Room'' and ''Little Big Worl'' . Muri ecran ya tereviziyo, yakoraga kuri serial ''The Lady of the Camellias'', ''Thicker than Water'' and ''Die Sonkring and Orion''. Some of her popular films include: ''Djadje'', ''Committed'', ''On the Wire'', ''Country of My Skull'' and ''Paljas.''  

